# Resolve all @geoman-io/* packages (incl. the Pro build) from Geoman's
# private registry instead of public npm. The auth token is read from your
# machine's pnpm config locally; on Vercel set GEOMAN_NPM_TOKEN and add a
# matching `//npm.geoman.io/:_authToken=${GEOMAN_NPM_TOKEN}` line there.
@geoman-io:registry=https://npm.geoman.io/
